original_title: 99 Cahaya Di Langit Eropa The Final Edition
overview: Europe does not just teach them about life science. But also pursue the Divine formula of diversity and enduring convictions. A tale of wanderings in discovering the great secret of human civilization thousands of years ago. Finding Islam, not only the faith and yet the practice.  This is the end of the trip Hanum and Rangga in Europe. Delivering them to the search for meaning and the source of truth Supreme perfect.
